reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought two of these for my kids’ new apartment. I made the decision purely due to next day shipping since I won’t be here long.Let’s get one thing out of the way. This is not a real furniture. The are 6 fabric boxes in a wood and metal frame. The top is quite solid, side is thin. The drawers are designed only to hold light items, ideally clothing. But for the price and speed of delivery, it is not bad.Another thing, this is a Chinese modular furniture. It comes with numerous parts and numerous hardware. Slow down and double check each step when you build it. If only fits one way. Too me two hours to build the first one, 45 minutes to build the second. I made mistakes with each. The most crucial step is make sure all the rails for drawers are facing the correct direction

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Smaller than expected but worth the price
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. It's definitely smaller than I expected but it still fits quite a bit. It's pretty nice for what you pay for. Kinda warped when I bought it so it was hard to put together but overall it's pretty good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Inexpensive but cute
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I really like this product it was easy to assemble although it took me hours to assemble, but I enjoyed putting it together. It's cute and will serve its purpose.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars A Dresser for Ants - Not worth the money
reviews.reviewText: It was my mistake to not check the measurements more accurately. This dresser is comically small. The product photos definitely make it look bigger than it is. It is not at all sturdy as the description states, it is very flimsy. I knew the drawers were fabric but I thought the front of the drawer was wood based off the photos not wood design printed on fabric. Very tackyThis dresser was also very time consuming to put together. My boyfriend put it together to surprise me and I wish I would have unboxed and told him not to waste his time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Read all the info before you buy
reviews.reviewText: The mistake I made was not reading all the information on this product. It looks really good but is very cheap, considering this was $120 I did not notice that it had cloth drawers. The angle in the picture on here makes it look bigger than it is. My picture shows you just tiny it looks on a wall. this might be good for children's room but not for adults. It's not sturdy and wobbles a lot. I don't see it lasting too long.Update: I was contacted by the seller after I posted this, and they offered me a discount. I accepted the officer. I was not going to take the time to take it apart and ship it back. I am very pleased with the quickness of their reply and the willingness to offer something back to make my displeasure better. It worked. I am changing my one start to a 3 star. I still have not started using this yet. Stars might change again once I see how it will hold my clothes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The best one
reviews.reviewText: The best drawer for the money. Excellent engineering, easy to put together, very solid and sturdy. In addition, it looks excellent! Highly recommend to everyone.
